# Project Structure

When introducing changes to the project, always follow the directory structure below:

- `./src` - source code
- `./src/api` - Hono server configuration and REST api endpoints
- `./src/assets` - code realated to erc20 assets
- `./src/vaults` - code realated to erc4626 vaults
- `./src/utils` - other code
- `./ponder.config.ts` - Ponder app config with configuration for chains, indexed smart contracts and database connection
- `./abis.ts` - ABI files
- `./containers` - Docker containers related files

When modifying the directory structure, always update this structure.




